            <p class="am-small" style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #999; margin-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;">
              AI Search Optimization &amp; Legal: <span id="amara-ai-status-indicator" title="Initializing..."></span>
